# Put your Weibo cookie string on ONE line below, then rename/copy to:
#   secrets/weibo_cookie.txt
#
# How to get cookie (from dataabc/weibo-search README):
# 1. Chrome open https://weibo.com and login
# 2. F12 -> Network -> weibo.cn -> Request Headers -> Cookie
# 3. Paste the Cookie value into secrets/weibo_cookie.txt
#
# NEVER commit secrets/weibo_cookie.txt
